OL,3,CGrant Shapps distances himself from
OL,4,CAnderson's comments about Khan
OL,6,FLee Anderson has been criticised by
OL,7,FConservative and Labour MPs for his
OL,8,Fcomments about Sadiq Khan, as ITV
OL,9,FNews' Political Correspondent Harry
OL,10,FHorton explains.
OL,12,FCabinet minister Grant Shapps has
OL,13,Fdistanced himself from the former Tory
OL,14,Fdeputy chairman's claim that
OL,15,F"Islamists" have "got control" of
OL,16,FSadiq Khan.
