OL,3,CGrant Shapps distances himself from
OL,4,CAnderson's comments about Khan
OL,6,FIn an appearance on GB News, Mr
OL,7,FAnderson had said: "I don't actually
OL,8,Fbelieve that the Islamists have got
OL,9,Fcontrol of our country, but what I do
OL,10,Fbelieve is they've got control of Khan
OL,11,Fand they've got control of London...
OL,12,FHe's actually given our capital city
OL,13,Faway to his mates."
OL,15,FThe remarks prompted criticism from
OL,16,FLabour and some Conservatives, with
OL,17,Fsenior Tory MP Sir Sajid Javid
OL,18,Fdescribing them as "ridiculous".
