OL,6,FTory peer Gavin Barwell, who was
OL,7,FTheresa May's Number 10 chief of
OL,8,Fstaff, said the remark was a
OL,9,F"despicable slur".
OL,11,FBusiness minister Nus Ghani,
OL,12,Fmeanwhile, said the comments were
OL,13,F"foolish and dangerous".
OL,15,FIn a post on X, formerly Twitter, the
OL,16,FWealden MP said: "I have spoken to Lee
OL,17,FAnderson. I've called out Islamic
OL,18,Fextremism (& been attacked by hard
OL,19,Fleft, far right & Islamists).
