OL,3,CGrant Shapps distances himself from
OL,4,CAnderson's comments about Khan
OL,6,F"I don't for one moment believe that
OL,7,FSadiq Khan is controlled by Islamists.
OL,8,FTo say so, is both foolish and
OL,9,Fdangerous. Frankly this is all so
OL,10,Ftiring..."
OL,12,FThe Muslim Council of Britain said the
OL,13,Fcomment was "disgusting" and
OL,14,Fcriticised the "silence of the party
OL,15,Fin the face of such extremism".
